<topic id='attribute_organisation_code.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Attribute: ORGANISATION CODE - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
An 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_organisation_code">ORGANISATION CODE</xref>
 is a code which identifies an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
 uniquely.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_organisation_code">ORGANISATION CODES</xref>
 are managed by:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                  keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
            <p>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                     keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">ODS</xref>)                </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_nhs_prescription_services">NHS Prescription Services</xref>
         </li>
         <li>
            <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_nhs_dental_services">NHS Dental Services</xref>
            <p>.</p>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                     keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
               <p>
codes can be downloaded from 
                                <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                        keyref="supporting_definition_technology_reference_data_update_distribution__trud_">Technology Reference Data Update Distribution (TRUD)</xref>
               </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                     keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_data_service">Organisation Data Service</xref>
               <p>
contact details can be found at 
                                <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                        keyref="supporting_definition_contact_details">Contact Details</xref>.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <b>
All NHS 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATIONS</xref>
 are coded using coding frames, as shown in the tables at: 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_organisation_coding_frames">Organisation Coding Frames</xref>.        </b>
  </div>
</body>
